{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_09_01",
  "title": "天動瑠依 1話 か、か、間接",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏祭り当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Summer Festival Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "会場、まだ夕方なのに凄く賑わってます\nお祭りって、こんなに沢山人が来るんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The venue is already bustling even though it's only evening.\nSo many people come to festivals‚ don't they?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "今日のお祭りは、日本有数の規模だからな\nこの後ステージが控えてるけど、緊張してないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because today's festival is one of the largest in Japan.\nYou have a stage performance coming up. Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 19.233333226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "今回は、私一人でのステージですからね\nお気遣いありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This time it's a stage performance by myself.\nThank you for your concern.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、大丈夫です。ソロで舞台に立つ機会は\n少ないですけど、ワクワクしてるくらいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm fine. I don't get many opportunities\nto stand on stage solo‚ but I'm excited about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "それは心強いな。瑠依のパフォーマンスで盛り上げて\n地方の人達にもアピールしていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's reassuring. Let's liven things up with your performance\nand appeal to the local people too‚ Rui.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9999998927
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、頑張ります\n……ところで、まだ本番まで時間がありますよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ I'll do my best.\n…By the way‚ we still have time until the show‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくなので、少しだけお祭りを\n見て回りたいんですけど……いいでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we have this opportunity‚ I'd like to look around\nthe festival for a bit… would that be okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9666665594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "時間はあるし、構わないけど\n分かった、それなら俺も一緒に行くよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have time‚ so it's fine.\nOkay‚ then I'll go with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "人が沢山いる場所に、瑠依を一人で送り出せないからな\n俺が一緒じゃ、あんまり楽しめないかもしれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't send Rui out alone to a place with so many people.\nYou might not enjoy it as much with me along though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 66.0999998927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありません！\nあ……大きな声を出してしまってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true at all!\nOh… sorry for raising my voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3475369826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.933333226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "別に、嫌とかそういうのはありませんし\n{user}さんがいてくれた方が安心です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that I dislike it or anything like that\nI feel more at ease when {user}-san is with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 83.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、早速ですけど見に行きましょう\nどんな出店があるか、楽しみですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's go take a look right away.\nI'm looking forward to seeing what kind of stalls there are.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、せっかくだしお祭りも目一杯満喫しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ since we're here‚ let's enjoy the festival to the fullest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5999998927,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5899.9949138,
          "startTime": 92.4999948065
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 92.2499948065
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 92.2499948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　{user}さん\nあそこにヨーヨーすくいがありますよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…! {user}-san\nThere's a yo-yo fishing game over there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 98.1999948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "あっちは射的です、本当に銃で撃つんですね\nやったことありますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's target shooting‚ they really shoot with guns.\nHave you ever done it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 104.3333281398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　あの子達が食べてるチョコバナナ\nとっても可愛く飾り付けがされていますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Those chocolate bananas that\nthose kids are eating are decorated so cutely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4999949138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 115.3339807709
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "どこの屋台で売っているんでしょう？　美味しそう……\nでも、りんご飴といちご飴も気になるし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Which stall is selling them? They look delicious…\nBut I'm also curious about the candied apples and strawberries…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.3339807709,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依？　声のトーンを少し抑えてだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rui? Could you keep your voice down a bit…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.56665893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 123.6999948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません\nつい、はしゃぎ過ぎてしまって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry.\nI got a bit too carried away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 128.4999948065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "あの……実は私、お祭りって、小さい頃に\n母に一度、連れて行ってもらって以来なんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… actually‚ I haven't been to a festival since\nmy mother took me once when I was little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.7666615804,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 137.3666614731
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルになってからは、今日みたいに\nお仕事で参加することは何度かありましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've participated several times for work\nlike today‚ since becoming an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "こうして一人のお客さんとして参加するのは\n本当に久しぶりなので、なんだか楽しくって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's been a really long time since I participated\nas a regular customer like this. So it makes me excited.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4666493733,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshimifes-03-night",
      "startTime": 151.0999825994
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_09_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか……なら、今日くらいは\n多少はしゃいでも構わないよ。俺も付いてるしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… then at least for today it's fine\nto get a little excited. I'm with you after all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.53331604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshimifes-03-night.webp",
