      "text": "伝統的なお祭りでも、いろんなフードがあるんですね\nあそこの大きなお肉の塊は、雑誌で見たことがあります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even at traditional festivals‚ there are various foods.\nI've seen that big chunk of meat over there in magazines.",
        "id": ""
