      "text": "あれはドネルケバブだな\n屋台で見るのは初めてだが、美味しそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's doner kebab.\nIt's my first time seeing it at a stall‚ but it looks delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.9999867756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
