      "text": "凄い……あんなに大きい塊を上手に切り落としてますよ\nそれに、見て下さい。あの塊、回るんですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing… they're skillfully cutting off pieces from such a big chunk.\nAnd look at that. That chunk rotates!",
        "id": ""
