      "text": "あっちには玉こんにゃく……山形の郷土料理ですね\nすみれならきっとここは外さないでしょうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Over there is tama konnyaku… a local dish from Yamagata.\nSumire would definitely not miss this place.",
        "id": ""
